5.2.7  U+DBFF U+DC00 = ed af bf ed b0 80 = "ï¿œï¿œï¿œï¿œï¿œï¿œ"                               |
5.2.8  U+DBFF U+DFFF = ed af bf ed bf bf = "ï¿œï¿œï¿œï¿œï¿œï¿œ"                               |
                                                                              |
5.3 Other illegal code positions                                              |
                                                                              |
5.3.1  U+FFFE = ef bf be = "ï¿Ÿ"                                                |
5.3.2  U+FFFF = ef bf bf = "ï¿¿"                                                |
